					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12055127#post-4284571</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12055127/scp-4507#post-4284571</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2019 15:40:36 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>aismallard</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4598089</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The exploration logs were enjoyable and atmospheric, and the connections to Japanese culture were good. However, as I went through the article, I had a hard time maintaining my suspension of disbelief. The fact that they sent in so many individuals before giving up, wanting to terminate defectors, and lapses in tone make it fall just short enough for me.</p> <p>Neutral vote.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
